# Configuration
@tenant = 1
@access-contract = ContratTNR

### Api-Schema unit : Récupération de tous les paths de la collection unit
GET {{url-access}}/admin-external/v1/schema/unit
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant}}
X-Access-Contract-Id: {{access-contract}}


### Api-Schema objectgroup : Récupération de tous les paths de la collection objectgroup
GET {{url-access}}/admin-external/v1/schema/objectgroup
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant}}
X-Access-Contract-Id: {{access-contract}}
